.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
The people have 5 different jobs:  architect, accountant, analyst, scientist, doctor
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
City: prague, edinburgh, hannover, nizza, hamburg
1. the british is the person who likes red
2. the swedish is the person traveling to hannover
3. the danish is the scientist
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the accountant
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the person traveling to edinburgh
7. the person who likes yellow is the dunhill-smoker
8. the analyst is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague
11. the person traveling to hamburgs is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the bluemaster-smoker is the architect
13. the german is the prince-smoker
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the doctor

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| City		|     prague	|    hamburg	|     edinburgh	|     nizza	|      hannover	|
| Job	|    doctor	|     scientist	|     analyst	|    accountant	|      architect	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
